<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../145/46145.xml">
Solaris</link></database>
</wordnet>
</lexical_database>
</electronic_database>
</information>
</message>
 and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../890/18890.xml">
Windows</link>. It has a centralized, cross-platform architecture allowing multiple systems to be easily monitored and managed. It was written by <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
<expert wordnetid="109617867" confidence="0.8">
