<sec>
<st>
 Software Components </st>
<p>

OSSEC consists of a main application, a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../982/33982.xml">
Windows</link> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../568/52568.xml">
agent</link>, and a <link>
web interface</link> software component.  </p>
<p>

<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Main Application: The main application, OSSEC, is required for distributed network or <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../878/17946878.xml">
stand-alone</link> installations.  It is supported by Linux, Solaris, BSD, and Mac environments.</entry>
</list>
</p>
<p>

<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Windows Agent: The Windows Agent is provided for <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../890/18890.xml">
Microsoft Windows</link> environments.  An installation of the main application configured for server mode is required to support the Windows Agent.</entry>
</list>
</p>
<p>

<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Web Interface: A separate web interface application provides a graphical user interface.  Like the main application, it is supported by Linux, Solaris, BSD, and Mac environments.</entry>
</list>
</p>

</sec>
